MAINSTREAM CONCEPT and TRAINING acquired from @chowenlai sir. Extremely grateful :")

Concept improvised by me makes you find the background setting, where, 
the more silhouetted you find me, the darker becomes my shadow, so you see her more in pain - reflecting what I'm hiding; 
facing my back at the daylight let's you know the energy in me which makes me embrace my fall and loss more than welcoming the brighter side - equally ready to embrace me; 
the less you find me clear here the less you see the movements, and the less you hear the song - you'll find raw emotions, you'll see less is more, you'll hear the vehicles passing by, birds crying along and my rough hands against the floor searching what I lost. 💌

Thanks to @rajnandini.pal for capturing it.

Since the month of May 2021, my life have seen a growth, an inclination towards what I always wanted to do. With the entire world quarantined it seemed like the universe giving me a *ME-TIME*, carving the path to a good teacher, to greater platforms, to meeting like-minded people who not only bring out the best in me, but also allows me to be a key part of their growth. They till date are the 50% reason why I have become a better artist and a better human. The teacher I have found and the dance style (that I could finally be sure about it suiting my artistic values and my body, sets me free of an ideal-dance-figure-mentality, sets me open and accepting people as friends irrespective of gender, size, colour etc) let's me underline the optimistic mindset I had initially -thereby nothing but just eventually broadening the same. 

So blessed to have discovered myself, analysed my desires, set my priorities- and more blessed and possible for the people, teachers, role models I have come across this year. 

THIS YEAR'S BEEN A BLESSING, PROBABLY THE BEST TIME OF MY LIFE. I CALL THIS AN ONSET TO MUCH MORE.

Max-Mueller Bhavan has got this quintessial library ever, covering nearly all genres - photography, architecture, art, comics, theatre. 
The Christmas tree, the community ideas and reviews, and essentially  when I could contribute a little from my side- the every dots and bits of it has not only made my day but have made me think if I would have missed this, probably the year would not seem to be this merrier!
This year nevertheless had been a blessing, but indeed its ALL'S WELL THAT ENDS WELL. 🌲

Celebrating Love, Acceptance and Self expressionism - I post /The Punking Folks/ in full-length for the first day of Pride month ! 🏳️‍🌈
Thank you for all the love on this. Truly special. ❤️🧿🙏

The Punking Folks :
Waacking and folk dance may seem worlds apart, but they share a common thread - community-driven expression. Both originated from marginalized groups, with wacking born from the LGBTQ+ community and folk dance rooted in cultural heritage. This shared spirit of self-expression and identity blurs the lines between them. I would like to be the medium through which you witness its intersection, forging an unique fusion, diversity and creativity.

Org : @prabhukunj_ @tithiiiiiiiiiiiiiiii
